  "text": "The metabolism of nandrolone is incompletely understood. Metabolites of nandrolone include 19-norandrosterone and 19-noretiocholanolone glucuronides that are detectable in urine [CITATION_1] . Animal studies suggest that nandrolone can also be converted to various estrogens via the actions of aromatase [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] ; however, human studies are lacking.",
